{
  "stem": "747.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from other town-- part of Hungary, where they were not in a ghetto, my father had an older sister.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In another part of the-- in the city-- in the country, sent us parcels.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Surprisingly, arrived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when how long-- how much we got-- everybody got a little bit from that it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't enough to keep us alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when they came the order that the following morning at six o'clock, we should be ready for relocation, and the order, again, that what we can carry with us, my father was relieved.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, at least we will be together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Hopefully, we will go to work and we will make it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Let's hope so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then my aunt said, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She's not going yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They divided the ghetto, 30,000 people, into 10,000 at a time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was three, three parts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my father said, I'm not waiting anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If we are-- if it's meant to leave, we will make it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It-- you can't live like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is not human.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Let's get it over with, and hope for the best.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we were into the first transport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They took us into the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everywhere, they used the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we-- we didn't sleep over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was just for a couple of hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they line us five in a row.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They marched us out to the railway station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What was very strange, that they brought the mental patients from the mental institution and they were a makeshift Jewish hospital.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took all the Jewish patients, all these patients, out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they brought them in wagons, and whoever, people have to carry them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they brought this all these sick people with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was somehow-- we started to speculate.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
